(3, 2, 'Tap Gold Crest', 'tap-gold-crest', '37 M T B ROAD PARALLEL TO J C ROAD NEAR MINERVA CI,BANGALORE,India', 'https://cdn.tourismcloudservice.com/HotelsV3/188780/201312594743410.jpg', 3, 'The 3-star Hotel TAP Gold Crest offers comfort and convenience whether you\'re on business or holiday in Bangalore. The hotel has everything you need for a comfortable stay. Free Wi-Fi in all rooms, facilities for disabled guests, Wi-Fi in public areas, car park, room service are on the list of things guests can enjoy. Comfortable guestrooms ensure a good night\'s sleep with some rooms featuring facilities such as television LCD/plasma screen, internet access – wireless, internet access – wireless (complimentary), non smoking rooms, air conditioning. The hotel offers various recreational opportunities. Friendly staff, great facilities and close proximity to all that Bangalore has to offer are three great reasons you should stay at Hotel TAP Gold Crest.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 413.78, 413.78, 1, '687961', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"687961\",\"twxHotelId\":\"908\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"TUA9WZyFgLBRcko65fwm\",\"hotelName\":\"TAP GOLDCREST\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"vv puram\",\"distanceValue\":1.63,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"37, Malvalli Tank Bund Rd, Near Minerva Circle, Journalist Colony, Kalasipalya, Bengaluru, Karnataka\",\"latitude\":\"12.9560634\",\"longitude\":\"77.5797214\",\"hotelRating\":3,\"total\":413.78,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTELS\",\"postalCode\":\"560002\",\"phone\":\"9845255494\",\"email\":null,\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tourismcloudservice.com\\/HotelsV3\\/188780\\/201312594743410.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Wi-Fi\",\"Bath\",\"Room Service\",\"Internet access\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":\"3.0\",\"tripAdvisorReview\":\"228\",\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:30:49', '2021-04-25 06:30:49'),
