(5, 2, 'OYO 10522 Varcity Emerald', 'oyo-10522-varcity-emerald', '12th Main Rd, KEB Colony, Madiwala, 1st Stage, BTM,Bangalore,India', 'https://www.hotelbeds.com/giata/66/663793/663793a_hb_a_002.jpg', 2, 'Varcity Emerald showcases outstanding rooms and comfortable stay making it worthwhile. Apart from basic amenities, this hotel also provides clean and spacious rooms with chic interiors and are well-furnished to provide the maximum comfort. These rooms are minimalistic with bright cushions and shiny curtains. Power backup, CCTV cameras and secured parking are among the other facilities provided to the guests. Many restaurants are nearby that the guests can visit and fulfill their appetite for food. Located in the outer ring road of Bangalore, the area is also well connected by all the means of local transport and one can visit famous tourist spots like Shiva Temple, Wari Watai, Shree Dodda Ganapathi Temple, Sri Maheshwari Temple and Lalbagh Botanical Garden easily from this hotel.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 600.3, 600.3, 1, '663793', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"663793\",\"twxHotelId\":\"871150\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"8rkIXiZq9ympw4gALKN7\",\"hotelName\":\"OYO 10522 Varcity Emerald\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"btm layout\",\"distanceValue\":5.96,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"12th Main Rd, KEB Colony, Madiwala, 1st Stage, BTM\",\"latitude\":\"12.917453\",\"longitude\":\"77.607491\",\"hotelRating\":2,\"total\":600.3,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTEL\",\"postalCode\":\"560029\",\"phone\":\"+919313931393\',+919313931393\'\",\"email\":\"amritesh.paramar@oyorooms.com\",\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hotelbeds.com\\/giata\\/66\\/663793\\/663793a_hb_a_002.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Wi-Fi\",\"Bath\",\"Room Service\",\"Internet access\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":null,\"tripAdvisorReview\":null,\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:31:01', '20