(7, 2, 'THE SIGNATURE INN', 'the-signature-inn', '479 O T C ROAD NEAR MASTAAN DARGAH COTTONPET BANGA,BANGALORE,India', 'https://i.travelapi.com/hotels/19000000/18920000/18913700/18913693/3f1c88fe.jpg', 3, 'The 1-star The Signature Inn offers comfort and convenience whether you\'re on business or holiday in Bangalore. Both business travelers and tourists can enjoy the hotel\'s facilities and services. 24-hour room service, free Wi-Fi in all rooms, 24-hour front desk, luggage storage, Wi-Fi in public areas are just some of the facilities on offer. Guestrooms are designed to provide an optimal level of comfort with welcoming decor and some offering convenient amenities like television LCD/plasma screen, mirror, towels, internet access – wireless, internet access – wireless (complimentary). The hotel offers various recreational opportunities. A welcoming atmosphere and excellent service are what you can expect during your stay at The Signature Inn.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 702.79, 702.79, 1, '680840', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"680840\",\"twxHotelId\":\"212789\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"t2V9K1RdczNbvfFUOkWZ\",\"hotelName\":\"THE SIGNATURE INN\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"balepette\",\"distanceValue\":2.06,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"479, O.T.C Road, Near Mastaan Dargah, Cottonpet, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560053, India\",\"latitude\":\"12.973076899999999\",\"longitude\":\"77.5705006\",\"hotelRating\":3,\"total\":702.79,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTELS\",\"postalCode\":\"560053\",\"phone\":\"080 40908204\",\"email\":null,\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/i.travelapi.com\\/hotels\\/19000000\\/18920000\\/18913700\\/18913693\\/3f1c88fe.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Internet access\",\"WLAN access\",\"Room Service\",\"Car Park\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":null,\"tripAdvisorReview\":null,\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:31:09', '2021-04-25 06:31:0