(8, 2, 'OYO 10480 Hotel PMR', 'oyo-10480-hotel-pmr', 'Behind Thalaserry Restaurant, Prashant Extension,Bangalore,India', 'https://www.hotelbeds.com/giata/66/663792/663792a_hb_a_002.jpg', 2, 'Hotel PMR is a popular choice among travellers looking for a hassle-free stay in the Whitefield area. This hotel is backed up with several amenities to make your stay comfortable. The spacious rooms feature soothing colour tones and wooden cabinets. The glass panels in the corridor give a pleasant view of the surroundings. The property is fitted with security cameras. Facilities such as power backup and card payment add to the convenience of the guests. For those travelling with their vehicles, the property also provides a parking facility. The food joints nearby offer choices from various cuisines and some flavourful local dishes as well', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 703.44, 703.44, 1, '663792', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"663792\",\"twxHotelId\":\"871194\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"Nl6wKd3OsAC8MyJDmuV2\",\"hotelName\":\"OYO 10480 Hotel PMR\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"whitefield\",\"distanceValue\":17.46,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"Behind Thalaserry Restaurant, Prashant Extension\",\"latitude\":\"12.984215\",\"longitude\":\"77.749005\",\"hotelRating\":2,\"total\":703.44,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Non-Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTEL\",\"postalCode\":\"560066\",\"phone\":\"+919313931393\',+919313931393\'\",\"email\":\"amritesh.paramar@oyorooms.com\",\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hotelbeds.com\\/giata\\/66\\/663792\\/663792a_hb_a_002.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Wi-Fi\",\"Bath\",\"Room Service\",\"Internet access\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":null,\"tripAdvisorReview\":null,\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:31:13', '2021-04-25 06:31:13'),
(9, 2, 'OYO 25121 Bns Lodge', 'oyo-25121-bns-lodge', 'Gandhi Bazaar Main Rd, Gandhi Bazaar, Basavanagudi,Bangalore,India', 'https://www.hotelbeds.com/giata/66/663927/663927a_hb_a_002.jpg', 2, 'For a cosy and homely stay, Bns Lodge is a fine property for visitors in Bangalore. Rooms offer a warm and welcoming feeling with minimalist decor and presence of comfortable wooden furniture. The bathrooms are also well-equipped with basic amenities. The banquet hall is well-decorated and spacious and can be used for functions and events. CCTV cameras and power backup ensure security and safety of your stay. Free Wi-Fi service is also offered by the hotel to stay connected with social media or to catch up with pending work. The restaurants located near the hotel offer delicious delicacies for guests to enjoy.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 719.84, 719.84, 1, '663927', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"663927\",\"twxHotelId\":\"871334\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"nFgTNr7QB52Gj8uH6zcK\",\"hotelName\":\"OYO 25121 Bns Lodge\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"basavanagudi\",\"distanceValue\":3.14,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"Gandhi Bazaar Main Rd, Gandhi Bazaar, Basavanagudi\",\"latitude\":\"12.944421\",\"longitude\":\"77.572402\",\"hotelRating\":2,\"total\":719.84,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTEL\",\"postalCode\":\"560004\",\"phone\":\"+919313931393\',+919313931393\'\",\"email\":\"amritesh.paramar@oyorooms.com\",\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hotelbeds.com\\/giata\\/66\\/663927\\/663927a_hb_a_002.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Wi-Fi\",\"Bath\",\"Room Service\",\"Internet access\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":null,\"tripAdvisorReview\":null,\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:31:17', '2021-04-25 06:31:17'),
(10, 2, 'OYO 24259 Hotel Blue Inn', 'oyo-24259-hotel-blue-inn', 'Bannerughatta Main Road, Near Jayadeva Hospital437,Bangalore,India', 'https://www.hotelbeds.com/giata/66/663923/663923a_hb_a_002.jpg', 2, 'Hotel Blue Inn is located in the Bannerugatta Road in Bengaluru. The nearest metro station is Jayanagar located only a few minutes away from the hotel. The Tipu Sultan Summer Palace, Begur Fort and Bangalore Fort are some other popular places that can be easily accessed by a cab. The room is a cosy setting with huge windows and mirror for dressing. There is a small wall mounted wardrobe for storage and bath area is neat and clean too. The hotel rooms have free internet connection, air conditioning and television. The eating joints in the area are Absolute Barbeque BTM layout, Tandoor Garden-the family restaurant, Narmadas Hyderabadi Biryani, Taaza Thindi, Panchami Garden and Vaibhav restaurant.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 730.49, 730.49, 1, '663923', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"663923\",\"twxHotelId\":\"871177\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"DxFEZytKsJkfCuO1VG7a\",\"hotelName\":\"OYO 24259 Hotel Blue Inn\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"gurappanapalya\",\"distanceValue\":5.42,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"Bannerughatta Main Road, Near Jayadeva Hospital437\",\"latitude\":\"12.920343\",\"longitude\":\"77.600305\",\"hotelRating\":2,\"total\":730.49,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTEL\",\"postalCode\":\"560029\",\"phone\":\"+919313931393\',+919313931393\'\",\"email\":\"amritesh.paramar@oyorooms.com\",\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hotelbeds.com\\/giata\\/66\\/663923\\/663923a_hb_a_002.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Wi-Fi\",\"Bath\",\"Room Service\",\"Internet access\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":null,\"tripAdvisorReview\":null,\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:31:21', '2021-04-25 06:31:21'),
(11, 2, 'THE IRIS INN BY BHAGINI', 'the-iris-inn-by-bhagini', 'No. 21, 22/ 3, Outer Ring Road,Mahadevapura, (Near Emc2 &amp; More Mega Store) ,Bangalore,  560048,Bangalore,India', 'https://i.travelapi.com/hotels/8000000/7400000/7399400/7399349/66f1b767.jpg', 3, 'Located in Indiranagar, The Iris Inn By Bhagini is a perfect starting point from which to explore Bangalore. The hotel offers a wide range of amenities and perks to ensure you have a great time. Take advantage of the hotel`s 24-hour room service, free Wi-Fi in all rooms, 24-hour front desk, express check-in/check-out, luggage storage. Guestrooms are fitted with all the amenities you need for a good night`s sleep. In some of the rooms, guests can find television LCD/plasma screen, internet access – wireless, internet access – wireless (complimentary), non smoking rooms, air conditioning. Access to the hotel`s fitness center will further enhance your satisfying stay. Friendly staff, great facilities and close proximity to all that Bangalore has to offer are three great reasons you should stay at The Iris Inn By Bhagini. <br />Guests over 5 years old are considered as adults.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 749.31, 749.31, 1, '258515', 'trx104', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"258515\",\"twxHotelId\":\"197314\",\"productId\":\"trx104\",\"tokenId\":\"NTc1MjYyLzIxODM4ODQ2MDQ4NTYzOTM2NjUvNTg3\",\"hotelName\":\"THE IRIS INN BY BHAGINI\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"mahadevapura\",\"distanceValue\":11.07,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"21, Mega Store, 22\\/ 3, Outer Ring Rd, Near More, Saraswathi Nagar, B Narayanapura, Mahadevapura, Ben\",\"latitude\":\"12.990969\",\"longitude\":\"77.6881121\",\"hotelRating\":3,\"total\":749.31,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTELS\",\"postalCode\":\"560048\",\"phone\":\"8067369999-Switch,9035016951-Mobile,9686195372-Mob\",\"email\":null,\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/i.travelapi.com\\