(12, 2, 'OYO 15695 Varcity Comforts', 'oyo-15695-varcity-comforts', 'Maruthi Nagar Main Road, Zuzuvadi, Madiwala, 1st S,Bangalore,India', 'https://www.hotelbeds.com/giata/66/663865/663865a_hb_a_002.jpg', 2, 'In the middle of the bustling part of Bangalore, surrounded by a state of local habitation is Varcity Comforts. The hotel offers the best view of mesmerizing natural beauty and modern-designed rooms with a regal combination of modern and compact furnishing. The rooms are spacious, clean and equipped with all basic amenities all the time. The natural light streams in the room from the window which is open to the mesmerizing view of an exciting market place and the city. The guest can avail the facility of free Wi-Fi to stay connected with the internet. Other facilities include CCTV cameras, card payment option and power backup. Various well-known restaurants are near the hotel to beat your hunger pangs.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 757.55, 757.55, 1, '663865', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"663865\",\"twxHotelId\":\"871134\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"dF43hIq8iGlJtOjPokLE\",\"hotelName\":\"OYO 15695 Varcity Comforts\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"btm layout\",\"distanceValue\":5.48,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"Maruthi Nagar Main Road, Zuzuvadi, Madiwala, 1st S\",\"latitude\":\"12.925808\",\"longitude\":\"77.615212\",\"hotelRating\":2,\"total\":757.55,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTEL\",\"postalCode\":\"560029\",\"phone\":\"+919313931393\',+919313931393\'\",\"email\":\"amritesh.paramar@oyorooms.com\",\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hotelbeds.com\\/giata\\/66\\/663865\\/663865a_hb_a_002.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Wi-Fi\",\"Bath\",\"Room Service\",\"Internet access\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":null,\"tripAdvisorReview\":null,\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:31:33', '2021-04-25 06:31:33'),
(13, 2, 'OYO 10218 Hotel Berry\'s', 'oyo-10218-hotel-berrys', ' Kadubeesanahalli, Marathahalli36, 1st Cross RdBell, Bangalore, IN,Bengaluru (bangalore),India', 'https://cdn.tourismcloudservice.com/HotelsV3/391085/201633014215592.jpg', 3, 'A plush, modern and comfortable stay await for guests at Hotel Berrys in Bangalore, with a range of amenities provided for a pleasant stay.The chic interiors of the rooms are charming with patterned wall deco, matching false ceiling, and wooden floors. Overall ambiance of the room is quite bright, vibrant and pleasant. Guests can avail the free WiFi service and laundry service on request. Along with these, parking and card payment facility are also available. This hotel offers conference room and in-house restaurant which are spacious, vibrant with beautiful decor where guests can hold their events and functions if needed. Additionally, guests can use the mini-theatre on request and watch their favourite movies or sports. Hotel Berrys is an absolute treat with modern comforts and services.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 824.24, 824.24, 1, '391085', 'trx104', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"391085\",\"twxHotelId\":\"323738\",\"productId\":\"trx104\",\"tokenId\":\"MTM3NjEyOTYvMjE4Mzg4NDYwNDg1NjM5MzY2NS8xODY4\",\"hotelName\":\"FABHOTEL MARATHAHALLI\",\"city\":\"Bengaluru (bangalore)\",\"locality\":\"kodbisanhalli\",\"distanceValue\":12.08,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"36, 1st Cross Rd, Kadubeesanahalli, Marathahalli, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560103, India\",\"latitude\":\"12.941915\",\"longitude\":\"77.6969895\",\"hotelRating\":3,\"total\":824.24,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTELS\",\"postalCode\":\"560103\",\"phone\":\"+9108860278884\",\"email\":null,\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tourismcloudservice.com\\/HotelsV3\\/391085\\/201633014215592.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Restaurant\",\"Conference Room\",\"Internet access\",\"WLAN access\",\"Room