(15, 2, 'OYO 12543 Maple Tree', 'oyo-12543-maple-tree', 'Ramdas Plaza, 5th Block, HBR Layout, Near Nagawara,Bangalore,India', 'https://www.hotelbeds.com/giata/66/663820/663820a_hb_a_002.jpg', 3, 'Hotel Maple Tree is known for their round the clock services. This hotel is backed up with various basic amenities to make your stay feel like home. If you are planning for a road-trip to Bangalore with your friends or your family in your car, this hotel will be the best suited for you as they provide a parking space. The hotel offers warm hospitality in a wonderful relaxed ambience and many other services that you will enjoy to have during your stay. Free Wi-Fi can be used to stay connected with social media accounts. CCTV cameras here ensure security of your stay. Local attractions like Amrutha Sarovar, Hal Heritage Centre and Aerospace Museum and Anjanadhari Apartments are very close to this hotel', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 824.73, 824.73, 1, '663820', 'trx109', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"663820\",\"twxHotelId\":\"871304\",\"productId\":\"trx109\",\"tokenId\":\"vzOj7PqYZpyKJaiA5Q1W\",\"hotelName\":\"OYO 12543 Maple Tree\",\"city\":\"Bangalore\",\"locality\":\"nagawara\",\"distanceValue\":8.68,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"Ramdas Plaza, 5th Block, HBR Layout, Near Nagawara\",\"latitude\":\"13.03559\",\"longitude\":\"77.628515\",\"hotelRating\":3,\"total\":824.73,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTEL\",\"postalCode\":\"560043\",\"phone\":\"+919313931393\',+919313931393\'\",\"email\":\"amritesh.paramar@oyorooms.com\",\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hotelbeds.com\\/giata\\/66\\/663820\\/663820a_hb_a_002.jpg\",\"facilities\":[\"Wi-Fi\",\"Bath\",\"Room Service\",\"Internet access\"],\"tripAdvisorRating\":null,\"tripAdvisorReview\":null,\"special\":\"\"}', '2021-04-25 06:31:57', '2021-04-25 06:31:57'),
(16, 2, 'Octave Hotel & Spa  Marathahalli', 'octave-hotel-spa-marathahalli', '143/1, Kadubeesanahalli, Opposite Prestige Tech Park, Marthahalli Outer Ring Road, Varthur (H), Beng,Whitefield,India', 'https://i.travelapi.com/hotels/11000000/10940000/10937200/10937120/738db925.jpg', 3, '<h2>Hotel Description</h2>\n<p>Octave Hotel & Spa, Bangalore is a boutique hotel with a distinct sense of class and design. The hotel is uniquely designed for modern business traveler, providing a warm and comfortable ambience including lavish rooms, delectable dining, spa and fitness centre, and world-class banquets.Hotel is conveniently located in the business district of Sarjapura Road, surrounded by shopping malls, restaurants, eateries, residential and commercial complexes. The hotel is located adjacent to Total Mall, and a walk away from Bangalore Central Cinemax movie theatre. Surrounded by several popular restaurants, the hotel is close to Wipro Corporate park, RMZ Ecospace, and Vrindavan Tech Village. The hotel is located 45kms away from airport and well connected to the bus stand.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 876, 876, 1, 'H!0523082', 'trx107', NULL, '{\"hotelId\":\"H!0523082\",\"twxHotelId\":\"304101\",\"productId\":\"trx107\",\"tokenId\":\"xbcf2ggccu74lfmontacafbqk4\",\"hotelName\":\"OCTAVE HOTEL & SPA MARATHAHALLI\",\"city\":\"Whitefield\",\"locality\":\"kodbisanhalli\",\"distanceValue\":12.12,\"distanceUnit\":\"KM\",\"country\":\"India\",\"countryCode\":\"IN\",\"address\":\"143\\/1, Kadubeesanahalli, Opposite Prestige Tech Park, Marthahalli Outer Ring Road, Varthur (H), Beng\",\"latitude\":\"12.942276\",\"longitude\":\"77.697426\",\"hotelRating\":3,\"total\":876,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"fareType\":\"Non-Refundable\",\"propertyType\":\"HOTEL\",\"postalCode\":\"560087\",\"phone\":\"+918046629900\",\"email\":\"RESERVATIONS_MTH@OCTAVEHOTELS.COM\",\"thumbNailUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/i.travelapi.com\\/hotels\\/11000000\\/10940000\\/10937200\\/10937120\\/738db925.jpg\